short_desc: ADCID cannot be blank
full_desc: Header variable ADCID cannot be blank

short_desc: ADCID must be a valid code in list_of_adcids
full_desc: Header variable ADCID must be a valid code in list_of_adcids
test_logic: IF ADCID is not in list_of_adcids

short_desc: PTID cannot be blank
full_desc: Header variable PTID cannot be blank

short_desc: FRMDATE_ENRL cannot be blank
full_desc: Header variable FRMDATE_ENRL cannot be blank

short_desc: FRMDATE_ENRL must be in mm-dd-yyyy or yyyy-mm-dd format
full_desc: Header variable FRMDATE_ENRL must be in mm-dd-yyyy or yyyy-mm-dd format
test_logic: IF FRMDATE_ENRL not in (mm-dd-yyyy or yyyy-mm-dd)

short_desc: ENRLTYPE cannot be blank
full_desc: Q1. ENRLTYPE (Assign NACCID or transfer?) cannot be blank

short_desc: ENRLTYPE must be an integer between 1 and 2
full_desc: Q1. ENRLTYPE (Assign NACCID or transfer?) must be an integer between 1 and 2

short_desc: ENRLBIRTHMO cannot be blank
full_desc: Q2a. ENRLBIRTHMO (birth month) cannot be blank

short_desc: ENRLBIRTHMO must be between 1 and 12
full_desc: Q2a. ENRLBIRTHMO (birth month) must be between 1 and 12

short_desc: ENRLBIRTHYR cannot be blank
full_desc: Q2b. ENRLBIRTHYR (birth year) cannot be blank

short_desc: ENRLBIRTHYR must be between 1850 and current year minus 15
full_desc: Q2b. ENRLBIRTHYR (birth year) must be between 1850 and current year minus 15
test_logic: IF ENRLBIRTHYR<1850 or ENRLBIRTHYR>current year minus 15

short_desc: ENRLEDUC cannot be blank
full_desc: Q3. ENRLEDUC (years of education) cannot be blank

short_desc: ENRLEDUC must be between 0 and 36, or 99
full_desc: Q3. ENRLEDUC (years of education) must be between 0 and 36, or 99
test_logic: IF ENRLEDUC<0 or (ENRLEDUC>36 and ENRLEDUC is not 99)

short_desc: ENRLGENMAN must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4a. ENRLGENMAN (gender man) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENMAN is not blank or ENRLGENMAN  is not 1

short_desc: ENRLGENWOMAN must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4b. ENRLGENWOMAN (gender woman) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENWOMAN is not blank or ENRLGENWOMAN  is not 1

short_desc: ENRLGENTRMAN must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4c. ENRLGENTRMAN (gender transman) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENTRMAN is not blank or ENRLGENTRMAN  is not 1

short_desc: ENRLGENTRWOMAN must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4d. ENRLGENTRWOMAN (gender transwoman) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENTRWOMAN is not blank or ENRLGENTRWOMAN  is not 1

short_desc: ENRLGENNONBI must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4e. ENRLGENNONBI (gender nonbinary) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENNONBI is not blank or ENRLGENNONBI  is not 1

short_desc: ENRLGENTWOSPIR must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4f. ENRLGENTWOSPIR (gender two spirit) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENTWOSPIR is not blank or ENRLGENTWOSPIR  is not 1

short_desc: ENRLGENOTH must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4g. ENRLGENOTH (gender other) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENOTH is not blank or ENRLGENOTH  is not 1

short_desc: If ENRLGENOTH is 1 then ENRLGENOTHX cannot be blank
full_desc: If Q4g. ENRLGENOTH (gender other) is 1 then Q4g1. ENRLGENOTHX (gender other specify) cannot be blank

short_desc: If ENRLGENOTH is blank then ENRLGENOTHX must be blank
full_desc: If Q4g. ENRLGENOTH (gender other) is blank then Q4g1. ENRLGENOTHX (gender other specify) must be blank
test_logic: IF ENRLGENOTH=0 and ENRLGENOTHX is not blank

short_desc: ENRLGENDKN must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4h. ENRLGENDKN (gender do not know) must be blank or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENDKN is not blank or ENRLGENDKN  is not 1

short_desc: ENRLGENNOANS must be blank or 1
full_desc: Q4i. ENRLGENNOANS (gender no answer) must be 0 or 1
test_logic: IF ENRLGENNOANS is not blank or ENRLGENNOANS  is not 1

test_name: At least one gender must be checked
short_desc: At least one of the following variables must be equal to 1: ENRLGENMAN, ENRLGENWOMAN, ENRLGENTRMAN, ENRLGENTRWOMAN, ENRLGENNONBI, ENRLGENTWOSPIR, ENRLGENOTH, ENRLGENDKN, ENRLGENNOANS
full_desc: At least one of the following variables must be equal to 1: Q4a. ENRLGENMAN, Q4b. ENRLGENWOMAN, Q4c. ENRLGENTRMAN, Q4d. ENRLGENTRWOMAN, Q4e. ENRLGENNONBI, Q4f. ENRLGENTWOSPIR, Q4g. ENRLGENOTH, Q4h. ENRLGENDKN, Q4i. ENRLGENNOANS
test_logic: IF ENRLGENMAN ne 1 and ENRLGENWOMAN ne 1 and ENRLGENTRMAN ne 1 and ENRLGENTRWOMAN ne 1 and ENRLGENNONBI ne 1 and ENRLGENTWOSPIR ne 1 and ENRLGENOTH ne 1 and ENRLGENDKN ne 1 and ENRLGENNOANS ne 1
comp_forms:
ENRLGENMAN

ENRLGENTRMAN
ENRLGENTRWOMAN
ENRLGENNONBI
ENRLGENTWOSPIR
ENRLGENOTH
ENRLGENOTHX
ENRLGENDKN
ENRLGENNOANS

short_desc: GUIDAVAIL cannot be blank
full_desc: Q5. GUIDAVAIL (Do they have a GUID?) cannot be blank

short_desc: GUIDAVAIL must be an integer between 0 and 1
full_desc: Q5. GUIDAVAIL (Do they have a GUID?) must be an integer between 0 and 1

short_desc: If GUIDAVAIL=1 (Yes) then GUID cannot be blank
full_desc: If Q5. GUIDAVAIL (Do they have a GUID?)=1 (Yes) then Q5a. GUID cannot be blank

short_desc: If GUIDAVAIL=0 (No) then GUID must be blank
full_desc: If Q5. GUIDAVAIL (Do they have a GUID?)=0 (No) then Q5a. GUID must be blank
test_logic: IF GUIDAVAIL=0 and GUID not blank

short_desc: PREVENRL cannot be blank
full_desc: Q6. PREVENRL (Previously enrolled at an ADRC?) cannot be blank

short_desc: PREVENRL must be an integer between 0 and 1, or 9 (Unknown)
full_desc: Q6. PREVENRL (Previously enrolled at an ADRC?) must be an integer between 0 and 1, or 9 (Unknown)

short_desc: If PREVENRL=1 (Yes) then OLDADCID cannot be blank
full_desc: If Q6. PREVENRL (Previously enrolled at an ADRC?)=1 (Yes) then Q6a. OLDADCID (Previous ADCID) cannot be blank

short_desc: If PREVENRL=0 or 9 (No or Unknown) then OLDADCID must be blank
full_desc: If Q6. PREVENRL (Previously enrolled at an ADRC?)=0 or 9 (No or Unknown) then Q6a. OLDADCID (Previous ADCID) must be blank
test_logic: IF PREVENRL in (0 or 9) and OLDADCID not blank

short_desc: OLDADCID must be a valid code in list_of_adcids
full_desc: Q6a. OLDADCID (Previous ADCID) must be a valid code in list_of_adcids
test_logic: IF OLDADCID is not in list_of_adcids

short_desc: If ENRLTYPE=2 (Transfer) then NACCIDKNWN cannot be blank
full_desc: If Q1. ENRLTYPE (Assign NACCID or transfer?)=2 (Transfer) then Q7. NACCIDKNWN (Is NACCID known) cannot be blank

short_desc: If ENRLTYPE=1 (Assign NACCID) then NACCIDKNWN must be blank or 8 (Not a transfer)
full_desc: If Q1. ENRLTYPE (Assign NACCID or transfer?)=1 (Assign NACCID) then Q7. NACCIDKNWN (Is NACCID known?) must be blank or 8 (Not a transfer)
test_logic: IF ENRLTYPE=1 and NACCIDKNWN ne (8 or blank)

short_desc: NACCIDKNWN must be an integer between 0 and 1, or 8 (Not a transfer)
full_desc: Q7. NACCIDKNWN (Is NACCID known?) must be an integer between 0 and 1, or 8 (Not a transfer)

short_desc: If NACCIDKNWN=1 (Yes) then NACCID cannot be blank
full_desc: If Q7. NACCIDKNWN (Is NACCID known?)=1 (Yes) then Q7a. NACCID cannot be blank

short_desc: If NACCIDKNWN=0 or 8 (No or Not a transfer) then NACCID must be blank
full_desc: If Q7. NACCIDKNWN (Is NACCID known?)=0 or 8 (No or Not a transfer) then Q7a. NACCID must be blank
test_logic: IF NACCIDKNWN in (0 or 8) and NACCID not blank

short_desc: PTIDCONF cannot be blank
full_desc: Q8. PTIDCONF (Confirm PTID) cannot be blank

full_desc: If Q1. ENRLTYPE (Assign NACCID or transfer?)=2 (Transfer) then Q6. PREVENRL (Previously enrolled at an ADRC?) must be equal to 1 (Yes)
